// ===================================================================
//  test_distributed_checkpoint.hexa — Distributed Checkpoint (#243)
//
//  Exercises both the low-level dcp_* primitives (shard map, full save,
//  delta save, async simulation, version tracker) and the high-level
//  task #243 dckpt_* API (create / shard_state / save_shard /
//  load_shard / async_flush / recover).
//
//  Run:
//    PATH=$HOME/.cargo/bin:$PATH ./hexa self/test_distributed_checkpoint.hexa
